00:12:17,248 --> 00:12:19,968
♪Ask how deep the dust of love runs♪

168
00:12:19,968 --> 00:12:21,312
♪How strong longing grows♪

169
00:12:21,312 --> 00:12:24,544
♪I play till the final note♪

170
00:12:24,704 --> 00:12:26,816
♪Let fate cut like a blade♪

171
00:12:27,181 --> 00:12:30,784
♪I bid you one last farewell♪

172
00:12:31,264 --> 00:12:35,155
♪I know not love's emptiness
nor hatred's pain♪

173
00:12:35,155 --> 00:12:38,144
♪When we meet again,
the snow will melt away♪

174
00:12:38,669 --> 00:12:40,704
♪One vow, so deep in love♪

175
00:12:41,024 --> 00:12:43,840
♪I'd give my life for it♪
